      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented verification test suite with version-controlled release. Configuration management records must be available for the simulation environment.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used with documented V&V test suite. Version control records confirm solver release 22.2.0 with full regression testing. Simulation input files under Git version control. SQA requirements for MRL 2 satisfied."
    },
    {
