      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate convergence on canonical benchmark cases relevant to rotating machinery and viscous flow. Published verification results acceptable.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has published code verification results for lid-driven cavity, rotating disk, and pipe flow benchmarks. Convergence orders consistent with second-order spatial discretisation confirmed. Adequate for MRL 2 assessment."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
