      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) < 5% on primary QoI (hemolysis index) at the nominal operating point.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed: coarse (4.2M cells), medium (11.8M cells), fine (31.4M cells). GCI on RH index: 3.1% between medium and fine meshes. Richardson extrapolation confirms asymptotic convergence. Medium mesh selected for production runs. GCI exceeds MRL 2 requirement; achieves MRL 3 threshold."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must be documented with measurement uncertainty quantification. Boundary conditions must be reproducible from experimental records.",
      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions documented per ASTM F1841 hemolysis protocol. Inlet flow rates measured with Coriolis flowmeter (±0.5% accuracy). Temperature controlled at 37±0.5°C. Hematocrit 33±1%. Boundary conditions extracted directly from experimental records with full traceability."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (RH index) must be computed consistently between model and experiment. Systematic bias must be characterised.",
      "rationale": "RH index computed identically for model and experiment using power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al.). Bland-Altman analysis shows mean bias of +4.2% with limits of agreement ±18.6%. Bias direction is conservative (model over-predicts hemolysis). Comparison methodology documented and repeatable."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
