      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI (relative hemolysis index) must be directly linked to the clinical decision criterion. Mapping from model output to decision must be explicit.",
      "rationale": "RH < 1 criterion directly maps to the regulatory acceptance standard for CPB devices (FDA guidance). CFD-predicted RH is the primary decision input. No intermediate transformation required. QoI relevance confirmed by clinical consultant review."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
