      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry — identical to COU device. Operating points span the full COU envelope (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Fluid properties matched to clinical blood analogue. Validation activities are directly relevant to the COU with no extrapolation required."
    },
