      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection must be justified against available experimental data for rotating blood pump flows. Hemolysis constitutive model must be documented with parameter source.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmark comparisons for centrifugal pump flows (Yakhot et al., Apel et al.). Power-law hemolysis model parameters from Giersiepen et al. with published validation data. Model form uncertainty estimated via comparison of SST and realizable k-epsilon predictions: RH difference < 6% across operating envelope."
    },
    {
