    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed are acceptable given MRL 2 scope and Class II device classification with medium model influence. Grid convergence study exceeds requirements (GCI 3.1%). Validation against FDA benchmark dataset demonstrates adequate predictive accuracy (mean bias +4.2%, conservative direction). UQ campaign confirms model robustness across operating envelope with flow rate identified as dominant uncertainty contributor. RH < 1 criterion satisfied across all 5 operating points. Credibility assessment team unanimously accepts the CFD model as fit for purpose for the stated COU.",
